pan></p>\r\n<p style=\"border-right:medium none;padding-right:0cm;border-top:medium none;padding-left:0cm;background:#fbd4b4;padding-bottom:0cm;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;border-left:medium none;padding-top:0cm;border-bottom:medium none\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:consolas\">            <span style=\"color:blue\">this</span>.Resources.MergedDictionaries</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border-right:medium none;padding-right:0cm;border-top:medium none;padding-left:0cm;background:#fbd4b4;padding-bottom:0cm;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;border-left:medium none;padding-top:0cm;border-bottom:medium none\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:consolas\">                .Add(Microsoft.Windows.Controls</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"border-right:medium none;padding-right:0cm;border-top:medium none;padding-left:0cm;background:#fbd4b4;padding-bottom:0cm;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;border-left:medium none;padding-top:0cm;border-bottom:medium none\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;font-family:consolas\">                      .Ribbon.<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">PopularApplicationSkins</span>.Office2007Black);</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nI have no clue what to do in VB.Net.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHopefully someone has some ideas what code to write where in VB.Net.<br>\r\nRegards<br>\r\n--<br>\r\nCarsten<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n",
